      <li>You do not need Epic integration, subject debit-card reimbursements, or institutional IRB services as part of the same vendor</li>
      <li>A formal validation package (VAL-PLAN, IQ/OQ/PQ, VAL-REPORT) for Part 11 documentation is important to your compliance team</li>
    </ul>

